  <brief_title>Effective Strategies for Dementia Care</brief_title>
  <acronym>WISDE</acronym>
  <official_title>Testing Three Interventions for Clinical Effectiveness in Long Term Care Residents With Dementia: Snoezelen, Structured Reminiscence Therapy, 10-minutes Activation. A Cluster-randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
